A Farewell To Conventional Arms

The Russian Ministry of Defense rocked the world again in mid-May of 2022 by asserting no less than TWELVE NATO countries were contributing to the bioagents development in Ukraine. It was a great chance to compare notes with the Russian MoD. <picturehttps://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd700597b-fdc2-46e5-b6f6-172e81b8d754_1125x991.jpeg I have eleven countries - many US locations including Ft Belvoir, Canada‚Äôs BSL4 Lab in Winnepeg, Holland‚Äôs  Erasmus Lab in Rotterdam, Germany‚Äôs Marburg U, France‚Äôs  Sanofi in Lyon, UK‚Äôs Porton Down in Salisbury, Italy‚Äôs SAIS in Bologna, Belgium‚Äôs rural labs near NATO HQ near Mons, Luxembourg NATO distribution center, Swiss ‚ÄúEurolab‚Äù at CERN, and Denmark‚Äôs ferret lab near Eric Traub‚Äôs Insel Reims. <picturehttps://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7fa260e2-6100-4449-ae8d-6292365e379d_1125x1116.jpeg George Webb interviews Balkan Wars expert and war correspondent, Igor Mekina . 

But which country filled out NATO‚Äôs dark weapons ‚ÄúDirty Dozen‚Äù?  As it turns out, the answer is Poland. 

I had been to Poland to report on NATO‚Äôs Farewell to Conventional Arms - the ACT - the Atlantic Command Command Transformation. I had covered the NATO General who was the head of the NATO ACT in Poland as the most likely NATO country adjacent to Russia to have a bioagents program. But I somehow missed connecting the dots to the German bioagents program in Marburg. <picturehttps://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff18a3e94-e2be-449f-8240-fcc4ed819b31_1125x1165.jpeg <picturehttps://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1ec3bb3-1d79-444f-9927-090b111549f1_1125x1283.jpeg Now we had the connective tissues with NATO General names between Italy, Germany, and Poland, not ‚Äúcountry level‚Äù accusations. <picturehttps://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa81dee8b-c8bf-43aa-a1f6-f004af742f95_1125x824.jpeg The Russians say they are going to publish 3,300 documents about the program in English  We are waiting for that. <picturehttps://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6219a93e-aa51-46af-9e01-3cc036b02815_1125x799.jpeg
